{
  "texts": [
    "To validate its effectiveness, we have conducted a series of experiments to address the following research questions (RQs):• RQ1: Is FinAgent outperforming current state-of-the-art trading agents and handling tasks that challenge other algorithms?",
    "• RQ2: What is the effectiveness of each component of FinAgent in contributing to its overall performance?",
    "• RQ3: Does the integration of augmented tools in FinAgent lead to a distinguishable improvement in its trading performance?",
    "• RQ4: How effective is the diversified retrieval in FinAgent?",
    "To conduct a thorough evaluation of FinAgent, we evaluate it across 6 real-world datasets."
  ]
}